{"title":"荐歌：如约而至（许嵩）","slug":"荐歌：如约而至（许嵩）","date":"2022-05-20T10:22:47.000Z","updated":"2022-05-20T10:23:50.301Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：如约而至（许嵩）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。520 愉快！周末愉快！本周的荐歌是《如约而至》，来自许嵩，发行于 2018 年。<br>","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>520 愉快！周末愉快！</p>\n<p>本周的荐歌是《如约而至》，来自许嵩，发行于 2018 年。</p>\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=573384240&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe><br><span id=\"more\"></span><br>这首歌可能是描述恋人，也可以是放在各种亲密关系的场景：朋友、亲人。</p>\n<p>所以，这首歌在我的音乐世界里占据了很重要的地位。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">作词 : 许嵩</span><br><span class=\"line\">作曲 : 许嵩</span><br><span class=\"line\">编曲 : Adam Lee</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">如果早知道那天是我们最后一面</span><br><span class=\"line\">我绝不会和你谈论琐事浪费时间</span><br><span class=\"line\">人生里看似偶然却又必经的告别</span><br><span class=\"line\">无约而至 无人可免</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">有一回置身某个似曾相识的场景</span><br><span class=\"line\">那一刻我忽然感应你就在我身边</span><br><span class=\"line\">过去、当下、未来未必确有其界限</span><br><span class=\"line\">或许爱能穿越时间 抵达永远</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">等到秋叶终于金黄</span><br><span class=\"line\">等到华发悄然苍苍</span><br><span class=\"line\">我们相约老地方</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">等到人已不再奔忙</span><br><span class=\"line\">等到心也不再轻狂</span><br><span class=\"line\">我们相约老地方</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">等到记忆只剩精华</span><br><span class=\"line\">等到笑容不掺伪装</span><br><span class=\"line\">我们相约老地方</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">等到释怀所有悲伤</span><br><span class=\"line\">等到体谅世事无常</span><br><span class=\"line\">我们相约老地方</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n","more":"<br>这首歌可能是描述恋人，也可以是放在各种亲密关系的场景：朋友、亲人。</p>\n<p>所以，这首歌在我的音乐世界里占据了很重要的地位。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">作词 : 许嵩</span><br><span class=\"line\">作曲 : 许嵩</span><br><span class=\"line\">编曲 : Adam Lee</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">如果早知道那天是我们最后一面</span><br><span class=\"line\">我绝不会和你谈论琐事浪费时间</span><br><span class=\"line\">人生里看似偶然却又必经的告别</span><br><span class=\"line\">无约而至 无人可免</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">有一回置身某个似曾相识的场景</span><br><span class=\"line\">那一刻我忽然感应你就在我身边</span><br><span class=\"line\">过去、当下、未来未必确有其界限</span><br><span class=\"line\">或许爱能穿越时间 抵达永远</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">等到秋叶终于金黄</span><br><span class=\"line\">等到华发悄然苍苍</span><br><span class=\"line\">我们相约老地方</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">等到人已不再奔忙</span><br><span class=\"line\">等到心也不再轻狂</span><br><span class=\"line\">我们相约老地方</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">等到记忆只剩精华</span><br><span class=\"line\">等到笑容不掺伪装</span><br><span class=\"line\">我们相约老地方</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">等到释怀所有悲伤</span><br><span class=\"line\">等到体谅世事无常</span><br><span class=\"line\">我们相约老地方</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>","categories":[{"name":"人文","path":"api/categories/人文.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"人文","path":"api/tags/人文.json"},{"name":"荐歌","path":"api/tags/荐歌.json"}]}